title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 19
description:
In this video we will look at the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace this week. Again a large number of  mission packs have been added which will help you become better flying in MSFS. But in addition to this a new large airliner has been made available the Airbus A340.  Besides these items a serious amount of new airports are available which will make flying flight simulator even more fun.
